#import "../../../../../shared/environments.typ": *

==== Participants

    - n=60 adults with ME/CFS (ages 18–60)
    - Mild to moderate severity (Bell scale 40–70)
    - Stable baseline for $gt.eq$4 weeks (no recent crashes)
    - Comfortable with structured monitoring and data tracking
    - Exclusion: Severe/very severe patients, recent major crash (\<3 months), active deterioration

